text: Physique is the makeup (build, constitution, figure, form, shape) of a person's body.Merriam-Webster Dictionary Constitution or body type refer to a number of classification systems used to empirically or theoretically classify the body shape of human individuals. ==Related pages== *Bodybuilding *Obesity *Physical attractiveness *Physical fitness *Underweight ==References== Category:Fitness Category:Physiques
